refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 arrayget_defined_functions
 boolexclude_disabled&true;



 Gets an array of all defined functions.

&reftitle.parameters;


  exclude_disabled



    Whether disabled functions should be excluded from the return value.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.0.0

     The default value of the exclude_disabled parameter
     has been changed from &false; to &true;.




    7.0.15, 7.1.1

     The exclude_disabled parameter has been added.

  &reftitle.examples;



    get_defined_functions example


<?php
function myrow($id, $data)
{
    return "<tr><th>$id</th><td>$data</td></tr>\n";
}

$arr = get_defined_functions();

print_r($arr);
?>


